  "prompt": "Is lendingtree legit?",
  "response": "Yes, LendingTree is a legitimate company that operates as an online marketplace for loans and other financial products. Founded in 1996, LendingTree allows consumers to compare rates from multiple lenders for various types of loans, including mortgages, personal loans, auto loans, and more. \n\nHowever, like any service, experiences can vary. Some users appreciate the convenience of comparing multiple options in one place, while others may encounter issues related to customer service or the terms offered by lenders. It's always a good idea to read reviews, check the terms and conditions carefully, and do your own research when considering financial products through platforms like LendingTree.\n\nIf you're looking into using their services, ensure that you're aware of any fees, interest rates, and contractual obligations before proceeding.",
